:49:32+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573379773"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573379773"&gt;銀主積極出貨，屯門居屋兆安苑兩房銀主盤，獲上車客於已補價自由市場以約310萬港元承接，低市價逾15%。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;原文網址：上車客搵樓半年310萬買560呎居屋低市價逾15% | on.cc東網 | 產經 &lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20250727%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20250727144423570-0727_00842_001.html%3Fkeywordid%3D4028828d7471d2a50174ba053e176f16%26keywordname%3D%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=0cc91d1cef67d075f012f458bb8ba57e&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/fina ... &amp;amp;amp;keywordname=地產&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31992281&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1989857727688621b73266d3_75071202"/><published>2025-07-27T18:49:32+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>f38a0c89892aec07b1d8cdc3e2aafba8</id><title>🆘蝕讓成交｜NOVO LAND 2房戶546.8萬元獲新盤向隅客即睇即入市 3年貶值11%</title><updated>2025-07-27T18:50:35+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-27T18:50:35+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573379784"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573379784"&gt;利嘉閣屯門兆康站分行高級分區董事胡志偉表示，新盤向隅客購入NOVO LAND 1A期二手2房戶，業主持貨3年，貶值11%。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;剛成交單位為1A期2座中層E室，實用474平方呎，以546.8萬元成交，呎價11,536元。單位放盤叫價570萬元，減價4%沽出，原業主於2022年以611.42萬元購入，帳面蝕讓64.62萬元，或11%。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;NOVO LAND 全部已經落成現樓，屋苑設施齊備，買家鍾情屋苑會所設施和新鴻基物業質素有保證，結果睇樓即決定購入。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F3984439%2F%25E8%259D%2595%25E8%25AE%2593%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BA%25A4%25EF%25BD%259CNOVO%2520LAND%25202%25E6%2588%25BF%25E6%2588%25B6546.8%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583%25E7%258D%25B2%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%259B%25A4%25E5%2590%2591%25E9%259A%2585%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%258D%25B3%25E7%259D%2587%25E5%258D%25B3%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25B8%2582%25203%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25B2%25B6%25E5%2580%25BC11-%3Fmtc%3D60037&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=4b4507a42c3b34a0b88da5364f813d42&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://ps.hket.com/article/3984 ... 市 3年貶值11-?mtc=60037&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31992282&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1989857727688621b73266d3_75071202"/><published>2025-07-27T18:50:35+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>bfeff084fb2703e4b9237efafa2ebb51</id><title>蝕讓成交｜區內客心儀屯門市廣場位於中心地段 386萬購入</title><updated>2025-07-27T18:51:06+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-27T18:51:06+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573379790"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573379790"&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F3984447%2F%25E8%259D%2595%25E8%25AE%2593%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BA%25A4%25EF%25BD%259C%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%2585%25A7%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%2584%2580%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%25A0%25B4%25E4%25BD%258D%25E6%2596%25BC%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BF%2583%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%25AE%25B5%2520386%25E8%2590%25AC%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E5%2585%25A5%3Fmtc%3D60037&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=2a7f3644eafb623cf71f530c1c337801&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://ps.hket.com/article/3984 ... 地段 386萬購入?mtc=60037&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;私樓成交&lt;br/&gt;撰文：麥穎華&lt;br/&gt;發布時間：23分鐘前&lt;br/&gt;區內客心儀屯門市廣場位於中心地段以386萬購入&lt;br/&gt;▲ 區內客心儀屯門市廣場位於中心地段以386萬購入&lt;br/&gt;祥益地產區域董事袁思賢表示，日前屯門市廣場錄得一宗買賣成交個案，原業主於2017年以約425萬購入單位，是次轉手帳面虧蝕約39萬或9%。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;上述所錄成交單位為3座中層G室，實用面積349呎，兩房一廳，日前獲區內客垂青。該買家鍾情上述屋苑位於屯門中心地段，購物、交通都應有盡有，而且單位附企理裝修，加上原業主有累減32萬的議幅，遂便決定以386萬購入自住，以實用面積計算平均呎價為11060元，屬市場價成交。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31992283&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1989857727688621b73266d3_75071202"/><published>2025-07-27T18:51:06+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>2fe9b232369eaf716d2eed4abde716fb</id><title>結業潮｜再多兩間酒樓執笠 明星海鮮燒鵝專門店黃大仙店8月結業</title><updated>2025-07-27T18:51:40+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-27T18:51:40+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573379799"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573379799"&gt;&lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F3983354%2F%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E6%25BD%25AE%25EF%25BD%259C%25E5%2586%258D%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%2585%25A9%25E9%2596%2593%25E9%2585%2592%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%259F%25B7%25E7%25AC%25A0%2520%2520%25E6%2598%258E%25E6%2598%259F%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E9%25AE%25AE%25E7%2587%2592%25E9%25B5%259D%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%2596%2580%25E5%25BA%2597%25E9%25BB%2583%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E4%25BB%2599%25E5%25BA%25978%25E6%259C%2588%25E7%25B5%2590%25E6%25A5%25AD%3Fmtc%3D60037&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=2e15249975b087348a4b40d1490c45c6&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://ps.hket.com/article/3983 ... 店黃大仙店8月結業?mtc=60037&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;近期多間酒樓相繼結業，近日再多兩間酒樓宣布結業，除了太子的金滿樓，以及由連鎖集團「明星海鮮酒家」經營、位於黃大仙竹園明星海鮮燒鵝專門店，亦宣告8月1日結業。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;有網民在facebook「香港酒樓關注組」中發文，指再多兩間酒樓結業，包括太子的金滿樓，以及黃大仙竹園明星海鮮燒鵝專門店，其中明星酒家的結業通告寫著「租約期滿」，將在8月1日（周五）結業，並感謝賓客一直以來的支持，建議賓客可選擇光顧同集團其他分店。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;結業消息引起關注，有網民指，似乎將會「換其他集團接手」，而有疑似熟客則表示「竹園呢間（明星）只做到街坊生意」、亦有網民稱「所有租鋪經營的連鎖店都是這樣運作的。租約到期，業績不理想的就不會續租，另尋鋪位營業，正常現象來」。&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31992284&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1989857727688621b73266d3_75071202"/><published>2025-07-27T18:51:40+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>5a5ef4bc37962febc1ab455145b9c4de</id><title>🆘移英業主食白果 720萬沽The Campton兩房 樓價四年倒退27.4%</title><updated>2025-07-27T18:52:06+08:00</updated><author><name>叔叔要不要</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-07-27T18:52:06+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_573379803"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_573379803"&gt;儘管近期樓市氣氛有所改善，但仍未能扭轉近年的跌勢。長沙灣The Campton一夥兩房單位，最新以720萬元成交，呎價15,451元。原業主居住英國，為完成交易特意回港簽約，持貨4年帳面虧損約271萬元，樓價大瀉約27.4%。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;美聯物業高級營業經理吳冠衛表示，上述成交單位為The Campton中層L室，單位實用面積約466平方呎，屬兩房間隔。據悉，單位獲買家720萬元承接，並計劃自住，呎價15,451元。&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;原文網址: 移英業主食白果720萬沽The Campton兩房樓價四年倒退27.4% | 香港01 &lt;a class="bburl" href="https://r.discuss.com.hk/link.php?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F60260250%3Futm_source%3D01articlecopy%26utm_medium%3Dreferral&amp;amp;platform=&amp;amp;uhash=7aea1b039934fbf8cde56916bc7c9e54&amp;amp;fid=110" target="_blank"&gt;https://www.hk01.com/article/602 ... utm_medium=referral&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31992285&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=1989857727688621b73266d3_75071202"/><published>2025-07-27T18:52:06+08:00</published